@@aDruid@@N

Druids are nature casters who channel the raw power of earth and
poison through their own bodies. Unlike other spellcasters, Druid
spells cost @@eHP@@N instead of mana, and each cast builds
@@aOvergrowth@@N -- a rising tide of natural energy that increases
both the power and the cost of subsequent spells.

@@WRemort paths:@@N Thornwarden (tank) and Wildspeaker (utility)
@@WAdept path:@@N Hierophant (requires both Thornwarden and Wildspeaker)

See also: @@WOVERGROWTH@@N, @@WSUBSTRATE PIERCING@@N
